   What is Salesforce? Cloud CRM Solutions
   Sales, Service, and Marketing graphic

What is Salesforce?

Salesforce is a suite of web-based CRM applications that help you find, win,
and keep customers. Learn more.


   The World's Leading CRM for Small Business - Salesforce UK
   myTrailhead graphic

Small business?

See how Salesforce can help you generate leads, drive sales, keep customers
happy, and grow.


